duties_responsibilities.duty: Contribute to project plans for enhancing data collection, processing, scheduling, onboarding, and managing relationships with school IT departments.
Work closely with Academics & Compliance and Customer Success team to execute essential data collection and data processing functions.
Provide school data integration support by writing, customizing, and testing ETL tools for specific schools.
Maintain documentation on customer data integrations and review and clean data sets submitted by school IT departments for quality.
Actively communicate with school IT departments regarding data formats, data issues, data deadlines, etc.
Be the data lead on sales calls with prospective school and district partners.

education_certification.credential: BS in Computer Science, Information Systems, Statistics, or another relevant field (Master's preferred)
